00:58.559 --> 01:00.426
My brother!

01:00.428 --> 01:02.327
Hey! Hi.
Hey, riley.

01:02.329 --> 01:03.495
You know, um...

01:03.497 --> 01:05.364
I want to thank you again
for believing in me

01:05.366 --> 01:07.399
And giving me the confidence
that I would be okay.

01:07.401 --> 01:09.368
I will always believe in you.

01:09.370 --> 01:11.437
And I will always be here.

01:11.439 --> 01:13.405
Thank you, riley.

01:13.407 --> 01:14.740
Hi.

01:16.110 --> 01:17.176
Hey.

01:17.178 --> 01:18.577
Hey.

01:20.047 --> 01:21.113
Hi.

01:23.217 --> 01:24.283
Wow.

01:27.455 --> 01:28.554
Hey, riley.

01:28.556 --> 01:29.755
Hi, charlie.

01:29.757 --> 01:31.390
-Charlie gardner!
-Stop it.

01:31.392 --> 01:32.858
Cheese souffle!

01:32.860 --> 01:34.760
Maya, we just got back.

01:34.762 --> 01:36.028
What could he possibly know?

01:36.030 --> 01:37.863
Who could have
possibly said anything?

01:41.368 --> 01:43.302
He made me.

01:43.304 --> 01:44.770
How did he make you?

01:44.772 --> 01:47.473
I was like,
"you wanna hear
a great riley story?"

01:47.475 --> 01:49.475
He said, "yes."

01:49.477 --> 01:51.977
I heard you and lucas
are just gonna be friends.

01:51.979 --> 01:54.379
Yeah, actually,
what we're doing is--

01:54.381 --> 01:55.547
I heard you're free.

01:56.484 --> 01:57.783
Are you free?

